videos.description: Columbia G Mike Smith's 38 points were not enough to complete the comeback in 2OT against a determined Harvard squad. The Crimson take it 77-73.
videos.headline: Highlights: Harvard 77, Columbia 73 (2OT)  - Via Ivy League
